data.description: All this home needs is new owners! This 3 bed 2 Bath home is in a nice quiet neighborhood. With fenced back yard,full auto sprinkler system.The Roof,furnace/air conditioner,and water heater are all less than 5 yrs old.Most walls have fresh paint,newer carpet and laminate.Whirlpool appliances in kitchen.Big screen TV in living room. A must see, this home is move in ready!!
